{"tid":1790153,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"notebook入水有冇得救","createTime":"2019-12-19T19:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T17:44:33.000Z","uid":199179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"544359cc73eb1be7ac1838e94804570565bdd232","tid":1790153,"uid":199179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:00:51.000Z","msg":"飲緊野唔小心倒瀉咗少少落個keyboard右邊<br />\n之後即刻搵紙巾印乾<br />\n部機一直都係開住 冇幾耐hang咗<br />\n我禁開機制令佢重開<br />\n之後都冇乜野 係個keyboard壞壞地<br />\n禁一個制會打兩個字出黎咁<br />\n我見好似冇乜事就上網search要點搞<br />\n見到啲人話濕水要熄機<br />\n我照做啦 點知熄咗就開唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕流流搞啲咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae96615c01e29a5e2bc18b65c5bb50109fccf9ad","tid":1790153,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=7f311a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4a8e32aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"339c7